 key data, brainstorming internally, and collaborating closely to develop a detailed project plan. To ensure your project is set up for success from the start, we then determine a\u00a0 competitor analysis, target demographics, and design specifications.<\/p>\n                          <\/div>\n                        <\/div>\n                                                                                          <div class=\"tab left-0 top-0 w-full\">\n                          <div class=\"content\">\n                            <p>Next, the wireframing phase, is where we develop detailed desktop and mobile wireframes to fine-tune site structure and user flow. To ensure we are all aligned, these are then all shared via Figma for your feedback.<\/p>\n                          <\/div>\n                        <\/div>\n                                                                                          <div class=\"tab left-0 top-0 w-full\">\n                          <div class=\"content\">\n                            <p>Finally, we move to the content planning stage, where we provide expert copywriting and image sourcing services to make sure your content hits the mark.<\/p>\n                          <\/div>\n                        <\/div>\n                                                                                    <\/div>\n                              <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n                                  <div class=\"item w-full pb-0 mb-layout\">\n              <div class=\"item-inner\">\n                                  <figure class=\"media add-parallax\">\n                                                              <img width=\"1069\" height=\"600\" src=\"https:\/\/www.cbwebsitedesign.co.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/02\/process-designing-poster.webp\" class=\"add-parallax\" alt=\"web design agency wireframing\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.cbwebsitedesign.co.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/02\/proce