                                                         <\/ul>\n                                    <div class=\"tabs relative mt-10\">\n                                            <div class=\"tab active left-0 top-0 w-full\">\n                          <div class=\"content\">\n                            <p>In the design concepts phase, we present a tailored homepage design through Figma, so you can collaborate with us and share your feedback.<\/p>\n                          <\/div>\n                        <\/div>\n                                                                                          <div class=\"tab left-0 top-0 w-full\">\n                          <div class=\"content\">\n                            <p>Once approved, the full site design phase begins with the cohesive style across all your web pages, ensuring consistency and flow.<\/p>\n                          <\/div>\n                        <\/div>\n                                                                                          <div class=\"tab left-0 top-0 w-full\">\n                          <div class=\"content\">\n                            <p>We will also integrate custom\u00a0 interactive visuals and animations to keep users engaged and bring the site to life.<\/p>\n                          <\/div>\n                        <\/div>\n                                                                                    <\/div>\n                              <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n                                  <div class=\"item w-full pb-0 mb-layout\">\n              <div class=\"item-inner\">\n                                  <figure class=\"media add-parallax\">\n                                                              <img width=\"1071\" height=\"600\" src=\"https:\/\/www.cbwebsitedesign.co.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/02\/process-developing-poster.webp\" class=\"add-parallax\" alt=\"web agency London coffee\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" srcset=