         <div class=\"subtitle mb-layout-xs\">\n            <svg class=\"icon\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\">\n              <use href=\"#dot\"><\/use>\n            <\/svg>\n            FAQ&#8217;s          <\/div>\n                          <h2>Frequently Asked Questions<\/h2>\n                      <\/div>\n\n      <!-- FAQ -->\n              <!-- Mark this block as an FAQPage -->\n        <div class=\"w-full sm:w-3\/5\" itemscope itemtype=\"https:\/\/schema.org\/FAQPage\">\n          <dl class=\"accordion is-open lg:mt-12\" data-chris >\n                          <!-- Each FAQ item is a Question, linked via mainEntity -->\n              <div class=\"accordion-item open\" data-cursor=\"hover\" itemprop=\"mainEntity\" itemscope itemtype=\"https:\/\/schema.org\/Question\">\n                                  <dt class=\"accordion-item-title\">\n                    <h4 class=\"long\" itemprop=\"name\">How long does it take to build a website?<\/h4>\n                    <div class=\"icon\"><\/div>\n                  <\/dt>\n                \n                                  <dd class=\"accordion-item-content\">\n                    <div class=\"accordion-item-content-inner wysiwyg\">\n                      <!-- Accepted answer content -->\n                      <div itemprop=\"acceptedAnswer\" itemscope itemtype=\"https:\/\/schema.org\/Answer\">\n                        <div itemprop=\"text\">\n                          <p>A simple brochure-style website might take 6-8 weeks, while a more complex site like an eCommerce store could take 12 weeks or more. The time frame for building a website depends on the size, complexity, and specific features you require and considerations such as if branding is required. Our team however can work in an agile way on projects with tight timescales and there are options to launch sites in phases, so if you\u2019re in a rush, do feel free to still reach out. <\/p>\n                        <\/div>\n    