  <\/div>\n                            <\/span>\n                          <\/div>\n                        <\/div>\n                                          <\/div>\n                  <\/dd>\n                              <\/div>\n                          <!-- Each FAQ item is a Question, linked via mainEntity -->\n              <div class=\"accordion-item open\" data-cursor=\"hover\" itemprop=\"mainEntity\" itemscope itemtype=\"https:\/\/schema.org\/Question\">\n                                  <dt class=\"accordion-item-title\">\n                    <h4 class=\"long\" itemprop=\"name\">What is the cost of a web design project?<\/h4>\n                    <div class=\"icon\"><\/div>\n                  <\/dt>\n                \n                                  <dd class=\"accordion-item-content\">\n                    <div class=\"accordion-item-content-inner wysiwyg\">\n                      <!-- Accepted answer content -->\n                      <div itemprop=\"acceptedAnswer\" itemscope itemtype=\"https:\/\/schema.org\/Answer\">\n                        <div itemprop=\"text\">\n                          <p>Our pricing depends on your project requirements, with flexible payments made in phases as the project progresses. Typically, our projects range from \u00a310k ($12.5k) to \u00a3120k ($157k), with an average cost of around \u00a315-20k ($20k-26k). We do have a minimum project size of \u00a310k ($12.5k).<\/p>\n                        <\/div>\n                      <\/div>\n\n                      <!-- Feedback UI is left as-is, not part of the schema answer -->\n                                          <\/div>\n                  <\/dd>\n                              <\/div>\n                          <!-- Each FAQ item is a Question, linked via mainEntity -->\n              <div class=\"accordion-item open\" data-cursor=\"hover\" itemprop=\"mainEntity\" itemscope itemtype=\"https:\/\/schema.org\/Question\">\n                                  <dt class=\"accordion-item-title\">\n                    <h4 class=\"long\" itemprop=\"name\">Will I retain full ownership of the design, development, and code?<\/h4>\n                    <div class=\"icon\"><\/div>\n                  <\/dt>\n                \n                                  <dd class=\"accordion-item-content\">\n                    <div class=\"accordion-item-content-inner wysiwyg\">\n                      <!-- Accepted answer content -->\n                      <div itemprop=\"acceptedAnswer\" itemscope itemtype=\"https:\/\/schema.org\/Answer\">\n                        <div itemprop=\"text\">\n                          <p>Yes! Once the project is complete and full payment has been made the website designs and all files will be delivered to you, and full ownership signed over. We don&#8217;t believe in retaining ownership or locking you into monthly fees.<\/p>\n                        <\/div>\n                      <\/div>\n\n                      <!-- Feedback UI is left as-is, not part of the schema answer -->\n                                              <div data-question-group>\n                          <div class=\"flex gap-4 mb-4\" data-question-ask>\n                            <strong>Did this answer your question?<\/strong>\n                            <span class=\"relative text-green cursor-pointer\" data-question=\"yes\">\n                              Yes\n                              <div class=\"faq-pop-up\" data-question-display=\"yes\">\n                                That\u2019s great glad we could help!\n                                <a href=\"\/contact-us\/\" target=\"_self\" class=\"btn btn-pink btn-small\" data-mp=\"\">\n                                  <span class=\"btn-bg\" data-mp-item=\"\" data-mp-scale=\"1.05\" data-mp-d=\"0.2\"><\/span>\n                                  <span class=\"btn-label\" data-mp-item=\"\">\n                                                                          Start a Project                                                                      <\/span>\n                                <\/a>\n                              <\/div>\n                            <\/span>\n                            <span class=\"relative text-red cursor-pointer\" data-question=\"no\">\n                              No\n                              <div class=\"faq-pop-up\" data-question-display=\"no\">\n                                No problem, one of our experts can give you a more in-depth answer.\n                                <a href=\"\/contact-us\/\" target=\"_self\" class=\"btn btn-pink btn-small\" data-mp=\"\">\n                                  <span class=\"btn-bg\" data-mp-item=\"\" data-mp-scale=\"1.05\" data-mp-d=\"0.2\"><\/span>\n                                  <span class=\"btn-label\" data-mp-item=\"\">Ask our Experts<\/span>\n                                <\/a>\n                              <\/div>\n                            <\/span>\n                          <\/div>\n                        <\/div>\n                                          <\/div>\n                  <\/dd>\n                              <\/div>\n                          <!-- Each FAQ item is a Question, linked via mainEntity -->\n              <div class=\"accordion-item open\" data-cursor=\"hover\" itemprop=\"mainEntity\" itemscope itemtype=\"https:\/\/schema.org\/Question\">\n                                  <dt class=\"accordion-item-title\">\n                    <h4 class=\"long\" itemprop=\"name\">What is the process for feedback, revisions, and approvals?<\/h4>\n                    <div class=\"icon\"><\/div>\n                  <\/dt>\n                \n                                  <dd class=\"accordion-item-content\">\n                    <div class=\"accordion-item-content-inner wysiwyg\">\n                      <!-- Accepted answer content -->\n                      <div itemprop=\"acceptedAnswer\" itemscope itemtype=\"https:\/\/schema.org\/Answer\">\n                        <div itemprop=\"text\">\n                          <p>Getting your feedback and ensuring the design perfectly meets your requirements is what our project managers excel at. We use industry-leading design tools like Figma and QA tools like BugHerd to make providing feedback to our team seamless. Our projects are carried out in phases and an iterative way, allowing for full feedback and refinement of your site until sign-off on your final, amazing site. <\/p>\n                        <\/div>\n                      <\/div>\n\n                      <!-- Feedback UI is left as-is, not part of the schema answer -->\n                                          <\/div>\n                  <\/dd>\n                              <\/div>\n                          <!-- Each FAQ item is a Question, linked via mainEntity -->\n              <div class=\"accordion-item open\" data-cursor=\"hover\" itemprop=\"mainEntity\" itemscope itemtype=\"https:\/\/schema.org\/Question\">\n                                  <dt class=\"accordion-item-title\">\n                    <h4 class=\"long\" itemprop=\"name\">What ongoing support or maintenance do you offer after launch?<\/h4>\n                    <div class=\"icon\"><\/div>\n                  <\/dt>\n                \n                                  <dd class=\"accordion-item-content\">\n                    <div class=\"accordion-item-content-inner wysiwyg\">\n                      <!-- Accepted answer content -->\n                      <div itemprop=\"acceptedAnswer\" itemscope itemtype=\"https:\/\/schema.org\/Answer\">\n                        <div itemprop=\"text\">\n                          <p>We&#8217;re flexible. We offer care plans, retainers, and ad hoc work tailored to your needs, ensuring you have the right level of support. A website is never truly finished, there&#8217;s always room for updates and improvements. We&#8217;re here to support you as your site evolves and grows, whenever you need us.<\/p>\n                        <\/div>\n                      <\/div>\n\n                      <!-- Feedback UI is left as-is, not part of the schema answer -->\n                                              <div data-question-group>\n                          <div class=\"flex gap-4 mb-4\" data-question-ask>\n                            <strong>Did this answer your question?<\/strong>\n                            <span class=\"relative text-green cursor-pointer\" data-question=\"yes\">\n                              Yes\n                              <div class=\"faq-pop-up\" data-question-display=\"yes\">\n                                That\u2019s great glad we could help!\n                                <a href=\"\/contact-us\/\" target=\"_self\" class=\"btn btn-pink btn-small\" data-mp=\"\">\n                                  <span class=\"btn-bg\" data-mp-item=\"\" data-mp-scale=\"1.05\" data-mp-d=\"0.2\"><\/span>\n                                  <span class=\"btn-label\" data-mp-item=\"\">\n                                                                          Start a Project                                                                      <\/span>\n                                <\/a>\n                              <\/div>\n                            <\/span>\n                            <span class=\"relative text-red cursor-pointer\" data-question=\"no\">\n                              No\n                              <div class=\"faq-pop-up\" data-question-display=\"no\">\n                                No problem, one of our experts can give you a more in-depth answer.\n                                <a href=\"\/contact-us\/\" target=\"_self\" class=\"btn btn-pink btn-small\" data-mp=\"\">\n                                  <span class=\"btn-bg\" data-mp-item=\"\" data-mp-scale=\"1.05\" data-mp-d=\"0.2\"><\/span>\n                                  <span class=\"btn-label\" data-mp-item=\"\">Ask our Experts<\/span>\n                                <\/a>\n                              <\/div>\n                            <\/span>\n                          <\/div>\n                        <\/div>\n                                          <\/div>\n                  <\/dd>\n                              <\/div>\n                          <!-- Each FAQ item is a Question, linked via mainEntity -->\n              <div class=\"accordion-item open\" data-cursor=\"hover\" itemprop=\"mainEntity\" itemscope itemtype=\"https:\/\/schema.org\/Question\">\n                                  <dt class=\"accordion-item-title\">\n                    <h4 class=\"long\" itemprop=\"name\">Will the website be mobile-friendly and responsive?<\/h4>\n                    <div class=\"icon\"><\/div>\n                  <\/dt>\n                \n                                  <dd class=\"accordion-item-content\">\n                    <div class=\"accordion-item-content-inner wysiwyg\">\n                      <!-- Accepted answer content -->\n                      <div itemprop=\"acceptedAnswer\" itemscope itemtype=\"https:\/\/schema.org\/Answer\">\n                        <div itemprop=\"text\">\n                          <p>Absolutely, not just mobile-friendly, but fully mobile-optimised. With mobile traffic now surpassing desktop, we design and wireframe the mobile versions of our websites from the start. We ensure your site looks and functions beautifully across all devices.<\/p>\n                        <\/div>\n                      <\/div>\n\n                      <!-- Feedback UI is left as-is, not part of the schema answer -->\n                                          <\/div>\n                  <\/dd>\n                              <\/div>\n                          <!-- Each FAQ item is a Question, linked via mainEntity -->\n              <div class=\"accordion-item open\" data-cursor=\"hover\" itemprop=\"mainEntity\" itemscope itemtype=\"https:\/\/schema.org\/Question\">\n                                  <dt class=\"accordion-item-title\">\n                    <h4 class=\"long\" itemprop=\"name\">Can I easily update the content myself?<\/h4>\n                    <div class=\"icon\"><\/div>\n                  <\/dt>\n                \n                                  <dd class=\"accordion-item-content\">\n                    <div class=\"accordion-item-content-inner wysiwyg\">\n                      <!-- Accepted answer content -->\n                      <div itemprop=\"acceptedAnswer\" itemscope itemtype=\"https:\/\/schema.org\/Answer\">\n                        <div itemprop=\"text\">\n                          <p>Of course. We use industry-standard CMS platforms, making it simple for you to set up and populate content for new pages in a flash. You can create a new landing page on our websites in the time it takes to make a cup of tea!<\/p>\n                        <\/div>\n                      <\/div>\n\n                      <!-- Feedback UI is left as-is, not part of the schema answer -->\n                                              <div data-question-group>\n                          <div class=\"flex gap-4 mb-4\" data-question-ask>\n                            <strong>Did this answer your question?<\/strong>\n                            <span class=\"relative text-green cursor-pointer\" data-question=\"yes\">\n                              Yes\n                              <div class=\"faq-pop-up\" data-question-display=\"yes\">\n                                That\u2019s great glad we could help!\n                                <a href=\"\/contact-us\/\" target=\"_self\" class=\"btn btn-pink btn-small\" data-mp=\"\">\n                                  <span class=\"btn-bg\" data-mp-item=\"\" data-mp-scale=\"1.05\" data-mp-d=\"0.2\"><\/span>\n                                  <span class=\"btn-label\" data-mp-item=\"\">\n                                                                          Start a Project                                                                      <\/span>\n                                <\/a>\n                              <\/div>\n                            <\/span>\n                            <span class=\"relative text-red cursor-pointer\" data-question=\"no\">\n                              No\n                              <div class=\"faq-pop-up\" data-question-display=\"no\">\n                                No problem, one of our experts can give you a more in-depth answer.\n                                <a href=\"\/contact-us\/\" target=\"_self\" class=\"btn btn-pink btn-small\" data-mp=\"\">\n                                  <span class=\"btn-bg\" data-mp-item=\"\" data-mp-scale=\"1.05\" data-mp-d=\"0.2\"><\/span>\n                                  <span class=\"btn-label\" data-mp-item=\"\">Ask our Experts<\/span>\n                                <\/a>\n                              <\/div>\n                            <\/span>\n                          <\/div>\n                        <\/div>\n                                          <\/div>\n                  <\/dd>\n                              <\/div>\n                          <!-- Each FAQ item is a Question, linked via mainEntity -->\n              <div class=\"accordion-item open\" data-cursor=\"hover\" itemprop=\"mainEntity\" itemscope itemtype=\"https:\/\/schema.org\/Question\">\n                                  <dt class=\"accordion-item-title\">\n                    <h4 class=\"long\" itemprop=\"name\">Will my website be optimised for search engines?<\/h4>\n                    <div class=\"icon\"><\/div>\n                  <\/dt>\n                \n                                  <dd class=\"accordion-item-content\">\n                    <div class=\"accordion-item-content-inner wysiwyg\">\n                      <!-- Accepted answer content -->\n                      <div itemprop=\"acceptedAnswer\" itemscope itemtype=\"https:\/\/schema.org\/Answer\">\n                        <div itemprop=\"text\">\n                          <p>Absolutely, this is one of our strengths as an agency. We have a dedicated SEO team involved in every project to ensure the websites we build are fully optimised to rank effectively from the start. Plus, we offer additional SEO services to take your site\u2019s performance to the next level and provide ongoing SEO to help keep you at the top of search engine results.<\/p>\n                        <\/div>\n                      <\/div>\n\n                      <!-- Feedback UI is left as-is, not part of the schema answer -->\n                                          <\/div>\n                  <\/dd>\n                              <\/div>\n                      <\/dl>\n        <\/div>\n          <\/div>\n  <\/div>\n<\/section>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"parent":0,"menu_order":1,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"footnotes":""},"class_list":["post-110","page","type-page","status-publish","hentry"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.cbwebsitedesign.co.uk\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/110","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.cbwebsitedesign.co.uk\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.cbwebsitedesign.co.uk\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/page"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.cbwebsitedesign.co.uk\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.cbwebsitedesign.co.uk\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=110"}],"version-history":[{"count":396,"href":"https:\/\/www.cbwebsitedesign.co.uk\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/110\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":15492,"href":"https:\/\/www.cbwebsitedesign.co.uk\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/110\/revisions\/15492"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.cbwebsitedesign.co.uk\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=110"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}